# Infra's API Secret Key — the value Infra prints on first boot
# ("API Secret Key is : ..."), or whatever you set as API_JWT_SECRET in
# platform/.env. The inflow-inspector-api verifies the panel's bearer JWT with it.
#
# You also paste this SAME key into the panel's Auth dialog (Shared Secret tab)
# to sign in — the panel signs an HS256 { admin: true } JWT with it.
INFLOW_INFRA_JWT_SECRET=
